StitchName: Small Quilted Cross-Stitch in Two Colors
Small Quilted Cross-Stitch in Two Colors
Repeat: sl 1 wyib, (k1, k1-b) in next stitch) k1, then pass slipped stitch over the last 3 stitches; p1
